PROBLEM_1 goal : Check ability to apply styling and understand selectors and box model.

Objective: Here I created an external CSS file and link it to HTML, Applied different text styles to headings and paragraphs and 
           Added background color and borders to a section also demonstrated margin and padding on a div for understanding its functionalities all these achieved based on the form I have created on DAY2 Hands On problem.

CODE:

--------------(p1index.html:)--------------------
    <!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Styled Webpage</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="p1styles.css">
</head>
<body>
  <h1> This the Main Heading</h1>
  <p>This is a sample paragraph with styled text. ‚ú®‚ú®‚ú®‚ú®üïµÔ∏è‚Äç‚ôÄÔ∏è</p>

  <section class="highlight">
    <h2>Section Title</h2>
    <p>Content inside the styled section.</p>
  </section>

  <div class="box-model-demo">
    Box Model Example
  </div>

  <form class="styled-form">
    <label for="name" required>Name</label>
    <input type="text" id="name">

    <label for="email" required>Email</label>
    <input type="email" id="email" placeholder="must have @">

    <label for="phone">Phone Number:</label><br>
        <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone"
               pattern="[0-9]{10}"
               placeholder="10-digit number"
               required> <br><br>

    <label for="Password">Password</label>
    <input type="password" id="password" required>

    <button type="submit">Register</button>
  </form>
</body>
</html>

-------------(p1styles.css)----------------

body {

      background-color: #cbb1b1;
}
h1 {
  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
  color: rgb(3, 3, 100);
  text-align: center;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

p {
  font-family: Georgia, serif;
  color: #851515;
  line-height: 1.6;
}

/* Section styling */
.highlight {
  background-color: #3d99e9;
  border: 2px solid #042a48;
  padding: 15px;
  margin: 20px 0;
}

/* Box model demonstration */
.box-model-demo {
  background-color: #7a82ef;
  border: 3px dashed#6d451c;
  padding: 20px;   /* inside spacing */
  margin: 30px;    /* outside spacing */
  text-align: center;
}

/* Form styling */
.styled-form {
  background-color: #cbb1b1;
  border: 4px solid #cda3a3;
  padding: 20px;
  width: 300px;
  margin: 20px auto;
}

.styled-form label {
  display: block;
  margin: 10px 0 5px;
  font-weight: bold;
 background-color: #cbb1b1;;
}

.styled-form input {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 8px;
  margin-bottom: 15px;
  border: 1px solid #aaa;
  border-radius: 4px;
}

.styled-form button {
  background-color: #4682b4;
  color: white;
  padding: 10px;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 4px;
  cursor: pointer;
}

.styled-form button:hover {
  background-color: #5a9bd5;
}



